Package algonquin.cst2335.finalproject.data

Class Flight

java.lang.Object
algonquin.cst2335.finalproject.data.Flight
public class Flight extends Object
Represents a flight entity with its details such as destination, IATA code arrival, terminal, gate, and delay. This class is used in conjunction with Room database to store flight information.
